detail.name: Shin
detail.effect: [On Play] Look at 5 cards from the top of your deck, reveal up to 1 card with 《Potara》 in its special traits and add it to your hand. Place the rest at the bottom of your deck in a random order.

detail.name: シン
detail.effect: 【登場時】自分のデッキの上から5枚を見て、特徴《ポタラ》を持つカード1枚までを公開し、手札に加える。残りをランダムにデッキの下に置く。
